{"word":"熬","detail":[{"title":"基本字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"熬"},{"type":"span","content":"āoㄠˉ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 烹调方法，把蔬菜等放在水里煮："},{"type":"span","content":"熬","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"白菜。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"熬"},{"type":"span","content":"áoㄠˊ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 久煮："},{"type":"span","content":"熬","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"粥。"},{"type":"span","content":"熬","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"药。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 忍受，耐苦支持：煎"},{"type":"span","content":"熬","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。"},{"type":"span","content":"熬","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"夜。"},{"type":"span","content":"熬","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"炼。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 古同“"},{"type":"a","content":"嗷"},{"type":"text","content":"”。"}]]},{"title":"英文翻译","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"cook down, to boil; endure"}]]},{"title":"详细字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"熬"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"āo","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈动词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)  (词源见 "},{"type":"span","content":"áo","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" 声) 把蔬菜等加水并放在文火上煮。如:熬白菜;熬豆腐"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2)  另见 "},{"type":"span","content":"áo","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"熬"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"áo","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈动词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1) (形声。从火,敖声。本义:煎干;炒干)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2) 同本义"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"熬,干煎也。——《说文》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"熬,火干也。以火而干五谷之类。——《方言七》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"淳熬。——《礼记·内则》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"设熬。——《周礼·小祝》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"何物中长食?胡麻慢火熬。——王建《隐者居》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(3) 又如:熬谷(干炒过的谷物);熬稃(爆米花)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(4) 用小火慢煮"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"太宗遣使取熬糖法。——《新唐书·摩揭陀传》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(5) 又如:熬粥(慢火煮粥);熬汤(煮物制汤)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(6) 忍受;忍耐;坚持"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"我心兮煎熬。——《楚辞·怨上》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"二则口渴难熬。——《水浒》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(7) 又如:熬不住(忍耐不了);熬不过苦刑"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(8)  另见 "},{"type":"span","content":"āo","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}]]},{"title":"常用词组","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"熬不过"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"áobuguò","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"不能忍耐支持到一定时间"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"熬出头"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"āochūtóu","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"忍耐支撑到了情况好转的时候"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"解放了,穷人总算熬出头了"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"熬更守夜"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"áogēng-shǒuyè","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"出于某种需要而彻夜不眠"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"熬煎"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"áojiān","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)比喻忧愁与苦难折磨"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"受尽熬煎"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"(2)也说煎熬"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"熬夜"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"áoyè","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"到深夜还不睡或一夜不睡"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"他们白天全有工作,要他熬夜,是不合情理的。——鲁迅《社戏》"}]]},{"title":"康熙字典","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【巳集中】【火字部】熬 ·康熙筆画：15　·部外筆画：11 "}],[{"type":"text","content":"【唐韻】五牢切【集韻】【韻會】【正韻】牛刀切，"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"音敖。【說文】本作"},{"type":"span","content":"𤏺"},{"type":"text","content":"。乾煎也。【揚子·方言】凡以火而乾五穀之類，自山而東，齊楚以往，謂之熬。【禮·內則】煎醢加于陸稻上，沃之以膏，曰淳熬。【周禮·地官·舍人】共飯米熬穀。【後漢·邊讓傳】少汁，則熬而不可熟。　又與嗸通。【前漢·陳湯傳】衆庶熬熬苦之。【註】愁聲。　【說文】或作"},{"type":"span","content":"䵅"},{"type":"text","content":"。【集韻】或作"},{"type":"span","content":"𩱏"},{"type":"text","content":"。"}]]},{"title":"说文解字","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【卷十】【火部】"},{"type":"span","content":"熬","class":["kszi"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"乾煎也。从火敖聲。"},{"type":"span","content":"䵅"},{"type":"text","content":"，"},{"type":"span","content":"𤎅"},{"type":"text","content":"或从麥。五牢切"}]]},{"title":"字源演变","content":[]},{"title":"同音字","content":[]}],"type":"通用字、次常用字","pinyin":["áo","āo"],"radical":"灬","stroke":"十画","total_stroke":"十四画","t_radical":"火","t_stroke":"十一画","t_total_stroke":"十五画","stroke_order":"一一丨一フノノ一ノ丶丶丶丶丶","input_method":{"bopomofo":"GKF","number":"58334","unicode":"U+71AC","wubi":"GQTO"}}